h.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdtyqn0X.jpg&h=5b1188cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEPEssD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEPEssD.png&h=64e3b05f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4898dc9eb4a3ffa07381a8bc4bcd52d0e240e278","tid":1610244,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"係妖怪邪神<br />\n拜佢老母"},{"pid":"66cb00023f67652775299c8d6fc129c9016bd9b7","tid":1610244,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"遇神殺神<br />\n殺邪神"},{"pid":"54f19f7231d72d17273d3dc679efb3f5ba6b7588","tid":1610244,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=333e4438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4ed97e5f6b0fa216c9096d3318862f50008a81","tid":1610244,"uid":67230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54f19f7231d72d17273d3dc679efb3f5ba6b7588","tid":1610244,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=333e4438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"可唔可以同神傾計"},{"pid":"523fa718864149d4b0f247db1a829fdf78e15e34","tid":1610244,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd4ed97e5f6b0fa216c9096d3318862f50008a81","tid":1610244,"uid":67230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote